<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Si abeka fehna hokʋt,
 Ʋba A̱ki Chihowa ma!
 Pit chi anukfihinli li;
 Auet is sa pihi̱sashke.

[V2]
 Sa nipi okʋt hotupa
 Yʋnha kia chinto fehna;
 Tikambi a̱ palʋmmishke;
 A̱ki ma! Et a̱ nukha̱kló.

[V3]
 Alʋm isht atia mak osh
 Chihowa i̱ yoshoba kʋt
 Na̱ palʋmmi moyuma ka
 Pihi̱sʋt aiasha yoke.

[V4]
 Ʋno ak osh Chihowa ya̱
 Im ai ashʋche li fehna;
 I̱ yoshoba li ho̱ mʋhli,
 Isht a sa nukha̱klo hoke.

[V5]
 A̱ki ma! A̱ kashofashke,
 Mikmʋt, si abeka hoka
 Is sa hlakoffichikbano,
 Ahnit chim ilbʋsha lishke.

[V6]
 Chi Shilombish Holitopa,
 Micha haknip ai achukma,
 Chu̱kʋsh himona aiena,
 Chim ahnit taloa lishke.</lyrics>
<aka>Si abeka fehna hokʋt, Abeka itonla im ʋba isht taloa.</aka>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Sickness ƲIT155</title>
<hymn_number>155</hymn_number>
<author>Cyrus Byington</author>
</song>